fuse: fuse (Filesystem In Userspace)
fuse:
fuse: FUSE makes it possible to implement a filesystem in a userspace
fuse: program. Features include: simple yet comprehensive API, secure
fuse: mounting by non-root users, support for 2.4 and 2.6 Linux kernels, 
fuse: and multi-threaded operation.
